<div class="paragraph">
<p>These variables are available in this container.</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>$BreadcrumbId — Contains the ID of the breadcrumb.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>$BreadcrumbLevel — Contains the breadcrumb level.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>$BreadcrumbName — Contains the name of the breadcrumb.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>$BreadcrumbUrl — Contains the breadcrumb URL.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>$DeepestBreadcrumbsLevelReached — Contains the information if the breadcrumbs' lowest level has been reached (true) or not (false).</p>
</li>
</ul>
